<PolicyPage ID="x63652" Name="On-Campus Pet Policy" Layout="general_Policy.xsl"><Title type="string" label="Policy Title" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false">On-Campus Pet Policy</Title><Abstract type="string" label="Policy Abstract" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false">Pets are not allowed in on-campus housing.</Abstract><Date type="date" label="Revision Date" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" display="localdateshort" UTC="true">20110301T07:00:00</Date><BodyCopy type="dhtml" label="Policy" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false"><![CDATA[<p>No pets are allowed at On-campus dormitories and apartments as well  as at University Village. According to the American Disabilities Act  (ADA), accomidations will be granted for service animals that have been  trained and certified.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
